These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, musical, martial-arts, spy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, rock, hip-hop, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, argentine, russian, malaysian
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, ship, snowmobile, motorbike
1. the argentine is the fan of pop##1
2. the russian is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person watching spy movies##2
3. the argentine is the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the fan of d&b is on the left of the australian##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
7. the fan of rock is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
8. the australian is on the far right##1
9. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | spy   | scientific  | martial-arts  |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | pop    | d&b      | hip-hop    |
| Nationality   | malaysian | argentine | russian | australian |
| Transport     | motorbike  | roller       | ship    | snowmobile     |

