.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, photography, puzzles, card-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, comedy, time-travel, animation
4 different pets are kept: turtle, mouse, fish, horse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, cricket, baseball, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the horse is the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person watching animation movies is between the owner of the fish and the person who's sport is skiing##2
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person watching animation movies and the owner of the horse##2
7. the owner of the turtle is on the far right##1
8. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
9. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | card-games | photography    | puzzles  | writing    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical      | comedy  | animation  | time-travel |
| Pet           | horse      | fish       | mouse      | turtle       |
| Sport         | cricket    | biathlon | baseball | skiing |

