.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, potato, orange, strawberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, collecting, dancing, filmmaking
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, accountant, chef, entrepreneur
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, tram, quad-bike
1. the chef is the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
5. the person eating orange is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
6. the accountant is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
7. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
8. the person eating lime is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
9. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person eating orange and the accountant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | potato | orange     | lime   | strawberry     |
| Hobby       | collecting   | skydiving   | dancing | filmmaking |
| Job         | architect   | chef | entrepreneur       | accountant    |
| Transport   | tram    | car | bike  | quad-bike    |

