.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, bartender, architect, manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, family, animation, horror
4 different pets are kept: lizard, goldfish, dog, rat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, swimming, tennis, skateboarding
 1. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching horror movies is the dancer##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching horror movies is the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 7. the person watching family movies is the architect##1
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 9. the dancer is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
10. the bartender is between the owner of the lizard and the manager##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | dancer  | manager | bartender     | architect |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | crime  | animation | family       |
| Pet           | goldfish       | rat    | dog      | lizard           |
| Sport         | climbing | swimming   | skateboarding   | tennis         |

