.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, apricot, cranberry, cucumber
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, journalist, dressmaker, entrepreneur
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, mystery, time-travel, thriller
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, surfing, cycling, swimming
 1. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1
 3. the dressmaker is the person eating apricot##1
 4. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
 6. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 7. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
 8. the journalist is the person watching mystery movies##1
 9. the person eating cranberry is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person watching western movies##2
10. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | apricot         | cranberry         | broccoli     | cucumber      |
| Job           | dressmaker | entrepreneur | project-manager    | journalist     |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | time-travel       | thriller    | mystery       |
