.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, coach, firefighter, police-officer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, disco, indie, classical
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, nigerian, brazilian, russian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, badminton, lacrosse, skiing
1. the fan of dubstep is between the person who's sport is skiing and the fan of indie##2
2. the coach is between the fan of dubstep and the russian##2
3. the brazilian is between the person who's sport is badminton and the nigerian##2
4. the firefighter is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the brazilian is the brazilian##1
6. the nigerian is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
7. the nigerian is on the left of the pilot##1
8. the fan of indie is on the far right##1
9. the fan of disco is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | firefighter | coach | pilot  | police-officer |
| Music-Genre   | disco      | classical       | dubstep     | indie      |
| Nationality   | russian   | nigerian      | brazilian   | mexican   |
| Sport         | lacrosse   | skiing    | water-polo | badminton   |

