 5. the spanish is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the chinese is the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the fan of trance is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
10. the german is the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
