4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person driving the scooter is between the person driving the skateboard and the person watching crime movies##2
6. the person drinking fanta is the person watching romance movies##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
8. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

