 1. the person eating banana is the analyst##1
 2. the person eating kiwi is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 3. the analyst is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 5. the fan of d&b is the person eating orange##1
 6. the fan of techno is on the far left##1
 7. the manager is on the left of the analyst##1
 8. the fan of disco is on the far right##1
 9. the scientist is between the coach and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
10. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating carrot##1

