.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, almond-milk, fanta
There 4 different types of food: avocado, peach, pepper, watermelon
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, cooking, traveling, board-games
4 different pets are kept: goat, hedgehog, bird, frog
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 4. the person eating avocado is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 7. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the owner of the frog is between the person eating avocado and the person eating pepper##2
 9. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
10. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person eating avocado and the person eating pepper##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | coffee    | almond-milk    | fanta      | iced-tea |
| Food       | avocado        | watermelon       | pepper       | peach     |
| Hobby      | traveling | puzzles | board-games | cooking        |
| Pet        | hedgehog       | frog     | bird         | goat           |

