 3. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 4. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 5. the owner of the pony is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the turtle##2
 6. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 7. the person who's sport is handball is the person eating peas##1
 8. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is the person driving the motorbike##1
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
